OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1775142707
OL,3,CCouncillors vote against plans for
OL,4,Chousing development on historic
OL,5,Cgrassland
OL,7,FCouncillors have voted against a
OL,8,Fcontroversial housing development on
OL,9,Fhistoric grassland in Bristol, in an
OL,10,Funexpected turn.
OL,12,FCampaigners from Save Brislington
OL,13,FMeadows cheered in a Bristol City
OL,14,FCouncil meeting on Wednesday, 1 April,
OL,15,Fas councillors rejected plans for 260
OL,16,Fhomes over wildlife concerns.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
