CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1775142707
OL,3,CCouncillors vote against plans for
OL,4,Chousing development on historic
OL,5,Cgrassland
OL,7,FOutline permission has already been
OL,8,Fapproved by the government's planning
OL,9,Finspectorate. As a result of the
OL,10,Flatest decision the developers will
OL,11,Fhave to resubmit updated plans.
OL,13,FThose will come back to the committee
OL,14,Fin a few weeks, but if councillors
OL,15,Fvote to refuse permission, that would
OL,16,Flikely be appealed, with the plans
OL,17,Fgoing to the government's Planning
OL,18,FInspectorate for a final say.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
