CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1775142707
OL,3,CCouncillors vote against plans for
OL,4,Chousing development on historic
OL,5,Cgrassland
OL,7,FAt the meeting, Janet Wren, from the
OL,8,Fcampaign group Save Brislington
OL,9,FMeadows, said: "It's our green lungs
OL,10,Fagainst the traffic pollution of the
OL,11,FBroomhill Road, the trading estate and
OL,12,Fthe Bath Road.
OL,14,F"It's our green space full of amazing
OL,15,Fancient trees, shrubs and flowers, and
OL,16,Fhas tonnes of wildlife and birds. It's
OL,17,Four place to support our mental health
OL,18,Fand the simple pleasures of taking
OL,19,Fchildren for a walk in nature."
OL,26,@qD@POU{D@_O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
