CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1775142707
OL,3,CCouncillors vote against plans for
OL,4,Chousing development on historic
OL,5,Cgrassland
OL,7,FIn response, Ben Leather, from
OL,8,FKeepmoat Homes, said: "We have worked
OL,9,Fhard to listen, not just to defend the
OL,10,Fproposal, but to improve it.
OL,12,F"Our purpose has been to work with
OL,13,Fofficers and local residents to shape
OL,14,Fthe best possible neighbourhood that
OL,15,Fcan be delivered on this site, for
OL,16,Fpeople who live nearby today and for
OL,17,Ffuture generations of Bristolians who
OL,18,Fneed a home."
OL,26,@pD@WOUzD@MO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
