PN,43405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1775142707
OL,3,CCouncillors vote against plans for
OL,4,Chousing development on historic
OL,5,Cgrassland
OL,7,FHe also told councillors that 30 per
OL,8,Fcent of homes would be affordable,
OL,9,Fincluding dozens of homes for social
OL,10,Frent. And , he stressed,the
OL,11,Fdevelopment would keep "significant
OL,12,Fgreen space" and improve biodiversity,
OL,13,Falthough this was questioned by
OL,14,Fenvironmental campaigners and local
OL,15,Fcouncillors.
OL,17,FOther concerns include a heightened
OL,18,Frisk of flooding due to the new
OL,19,Fhouses, and extra congestion on the
OL,20,Fnearby A4 Bath Road, a major commuter
OL,21,Froute.
OL,26,@sD@XOUtD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
