PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1775142707
OL,3,CCouncillors vote against plans for
OL,4,Chousing development on historic
OL,5,Cgrassland
OL,7,FThe meadows were sold by the council
OL,8,Fto Homes England, which then unveiled
OL,9,Fplans for 260 homes in November 2021.
OL,10,FAn outline planning application was
OL,11,Fsubmitted in April 2022, which was
OL,12,Fapproved by the Planning Inspectorate
OL,13,Fin April 2023.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
